OL,3,C'The sea saved me - now my story has
OL,4,Cbeen turned into a film to inspire
OL,5,Cothers'
OL,7,FReporter Katie Cole met Kathleen to
OL,8,Ffind out what it was like to see her
OL,9,Fjourney played out in animation.
OL,11,FA woman who believes Seaham beach and
OL,12,Fthe North Sea saved her life has
OL,13,Finspired an animation film to give
OL,14,Fhope to others.
OL,16,FKathleen Wotton began swimming four
OL,17,Fyears ago during lockdown, to help her
OL,18,Flipodema - a painful condition which
OL,19,Fcauses an abnormal build up of fat.
