OL,3,C'The sea saved me - now my story has
OL,4,Cbeen turned into a film to inspire
OL,5,Cothers'
OL,7,FNow Ellie Land has led a team of
OL,8,Fanimators to create a film based on
OL,9,FKathleen, which has been funded by the
OL,10,FBritish Film Institute.
OL,12,FThe animator approached the County
OL,13,FDurham swimmer after reading her
OL,14,Fonline blog, which documents her
OL,15,Fjourney.
OL,17,FAfter seeing the animation- named
OL,18,FPlunge - Kathleen said: "I kind of
OL,19,Ffelt like I was listening to it as
OL,20,Fanother person.
