OL,3,C'The sea saved me - now my story has
OL,4,Cbeen turned into a film to inspire
OL,5,Cothers'
OL,7,F"It really choked me up. I was like,
OL,8,Fthat's me who said that, that's my
OL,9,Fstory, and I didn't realise how
OL,10,Fpowerful it could be."
OL,12,FShe added: "Life's hard and when
OL,13,Fyou're at your lowest never give up,
OL,14,Fbecause at that last moment you might
OL,15,Fjust find your sport like I did."
OL,17,FSince she started swimming she has
OL,18,Flost a staggering 20 stone, and
OL,19,Fcelebrated her 50th birthday,
OL,20,Fsomething she did not think she would
OL,21,Fsee.
