OL,3,C'The sea saved me - now my story has
OL,4,Cbeen turned into a film to inspire
OL,5,Cothers'
OL,7,FShe credits the activity with saving
OL,8,Fher life, saying: "I feel alive when
OL,9,FI'm here... It means everything to me,
OL,10,Fit's a new lifeline. If I didn't come
OL,11,Fback and see my sister swimming here
OL,12,F(Seaham Beach), I wouldn't be here, so
OL,13,Fit's everything."
OL,15,FPlunge will get its premiere in
OL,16,FEdinburgh on Saturday 17 August, and
OL,17,Finternational festivals are already
OL,18,Fshowing interest.
