OL,3,C'The sea saved me - now my story has
OL,4,Cbeen turned into a film to inspire
OL,5,Cothers'
OL,7,FEllie said: "Kathleen's story and
OL,8,FKathleen's approach to life is really
OL,9,Fcourageous. I've known her for about
OL,10,Ftwo years and I've really seen her go
OL,11,Fthrough lots of ups and downs.
OL,13,F"I've always seen her bounce back, get
OL,14,Fback in the water, and I think her
OL,15,Fresilience and courage is really
OL,16,Finspiring."
